L at room temperature, we can easily find the number of molecules in the
 reactor:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
N_{reactor}=\frac{240\times10^{-9}\,\mbox{L}}{24\mbox{L}}N_{A}=10^{-8}\cdot N_{A}=6\times10^{15}\,\mbox{molecules}
\]

\end_inset

giving a residence time of 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
T_{res}=\frac{6\times10^{15}}{3\times10^{14}\mbox{s}^{-1}}=20\,\mbox{s}
\]

\end_inset


