The file is parsed from the top towards to bottom.
 All actions stated between individual 'time' commands is executed at the
 same time.
 At each 'time' command the flow is kept constant at the current configuration
 for the stated amount of minutes.
 The code-example above will thus start out by evacuating the sample for
 30 minutes before it start a flow of 5
